<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Trust & Safety</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
      }

      header {
        background-color: #333;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      nav {
        display: inline-block;
      }

      nav ul {
        list-style-type: none;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      nav li {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-right: 20px;
      }

      nav a {
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      main {
        padding: 20px;
      }

      section {
        margin-bottom: 40px;
      }

      h1,
      h2 {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('navbar',{user}); %>
    <main>
      <section>
        <h2>Buy a Property</h2>
        <p>
          If you're looking to buy a property, our website offers a variety of search options to
          help you find the perfect home. You can search by location, price range, property type,
          and more. Once you find a property you're interested in, simply contact the seller to
          arrange a viewing.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Sell a Property</h2>
        <p>
          If you're looking to sell a property, our website makes it easy to list your home and
          connect with potential buyers. You can create a detailed listing with photos and
          descriptions of your property, and interested buyers can contact you directly through the
          website.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Rent a Property</h2>
        <p>
          If you're looking to rent a property, our website has a variety of rental options
          available. You can search by location, price range, property type, and more. Once you find
          a rental you're interested in, simply contact the landlord or property manager to arrange
          a viewing.
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <%- include('footer',{user}); %>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
